product_name: Delkin Devices UHS-1 Class 10 microSD Card - 32GB
long_description: The 32GB Delkin Devices UHS-1 Class 10 microSD card is the smallest removable storage available, optimized for compatible action cams, smartphones, digital cameras, GPS and other handheld devices. Memory card offers reliable storage for media-rich applications, including high-definition photos, MP3s and even full 1080p videos. Included SD adapter lets you swap the microSD card from mobile phone to camera or any other SD compatible host for easy file sharing and transfer. UHS-1 Class 10 Micro SD. UHS-1 mode has a read speed of 56 MB per second and a write speed of 40 MB per second; Class 10 mode has a read speed of 22 MB per second and a write speed of 20 MB per second.
